Installation Notes:
===================

To build and run this program, simply do the following:

1. make
2. ./covert -h

Running as a Server:
====================

In order for both the client and server to communicate, the window size (-w)
needs to be identical on both sides.

NOTE: As a server, the destination IP address and port number have no effect.

./covert -s -f save_file_name -w 31415


Running as a Client:
====================

./covert -f read_file_name -d 192.168.1.1 -p 1234 -w 31415
